WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.389
Good morning, family. I just wanted to

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:04.070
come on and thank you all for

00:00:04.080 --> 00:00:06.309
all your love, support,

00:00:06.319 --> 00:00:08.150
shares, and everything you've been

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:10.870
doing to support me. I just

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:11.990
want to say thank you

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:13.509
from the bottom of my heart.

00:00:13.519 --> 00:00:15.270
You're helping get the

00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:18.310
gospel out there, and if it wasn't for

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:20.790
you all, this channel wouldn't exist. Besides

00:00:20.790 --> 00:00:20.800
the

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:22.150
Lord

00:00:22.150 --> 00:00:22.160
telling

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:24.230
me to do it, it takes

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:25.990
people to support it. I just wanted to

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.830
say thank you. I have some things

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:30.150
on my heart today to tell you

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:32.229
all. I know a lot

00:00:32.239 --> 00:00:33.830
of you are hungry

00:00:33.830 --> 00:00:33.840
and

00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:36.870
searching for answers for

00:00:36.880 --> 00:00:39.190
your own

00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:41.430
lives.

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:42.790
A lot of you are just

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:45.750
desperate, and I believe that I

00:00:45.750 --> 00:00:45.760
have many

00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:47.270
things I can help you

00:00:47.280 --> 00:00:50.150
with. My wife and I have lived by

00:00:50.160 --> 00:00:52.709
faith our entire

00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:55.110
marriage. I was raised this way, and she was

00:00:55.120 --> 00:00:57.990
raised this way: to live by the Word and

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.630
to stand on our covenant to believe for

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:04.229
the impossible. I have

00:01:04.239 --> 00:01:06.070
so many testimonies and things that

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:08.710
I can share with you about what the

00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:10.550
Lord has done for and

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:13.350
through us. Here is another thing

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:15.750
the Lord reminded me of

00:01:15.750 --> 00:01:15.760
while

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:18.310
I was praying. I asked, 'Lord, what

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:21.030
direction do you want me to go today for

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:22.950
the

00:01:22.950 --> 00:01:22.960
people?'and

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:24.550
He said, 'I just want you to keep

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:27.030
teaching them their authority—who they

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:29.510
are in Me, what they

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.510
have, and what I did for them on the

00:01:31.520 --> 00:01:33.749
cross, Brandon. A lot of them do not know.'I had

00:01:33.749 --> 00:01:33.759
forgotten about

00:01:33.759 --> 00:01:37.190
this,

00:01:37.190 --> 00:01:37.200
but

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.749
He reminded me.

00:01:44.720 --> 00:01:47.109
It started out this way:

00:01:47.119 --> 00:01:49.510
my wife was pregnant with our

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:53.030
first child. She

00:01:53.030 --> 00:01:53.040
was nervous

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:55.030
about the birthing process

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:58.389
because it was her first child

00:01:58.399 --> 00:02:00.069
and she didn't know what to

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:02.789
expect. As a

00:02:02.799 --> 00:02:05.270
first-time mom, she found a book called

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:07.429
'Supernatural Childbirth'and started

00:02:10.160 --> 00:02:12.309
meditating on the scriptures the

00:02:12.309 --> 00:02:12.319
author discussed

00:02:12.319 --> 00:02:14.630
about

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:18.869
how you could go

00:02:18.869 --> 00:02:18.879
through

00:02:18.879 --> 00:02:21.910
labor without any pain. She found

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:23.990
scriptures about the

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.070
children of Israel, noting that the Egyptian

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:27.990
women marveled because the women weren't

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.070
in any pain and their birthing

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:32.309
process was different. I

00:02:32.309 --> 00:02:32.319
told her,

00:02:32.319 --> 00:02:34.630
'I'll

00:02:34.640 --> 00:02:36.550
stand with you. I'll believe that there

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:39.190
will be no pain whenever you have the

00:02:39.190 --> 00:02:39.200
baby.'She

00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:41.430
was pregnant with our

00:02:41.440 --> 00:02:43.589
daughter at the time. She believed she

00:02:43.599 --> 00:02:45.430
started going into labor, but she supernaturally didn't

00:02:45.440 --> 00:02:48.150
feel any pain. This

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:49.910
is how it all started. I don't want

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:52.470
to shortcut the story of what

00:02:52.480 --> 00:02:54.869
the Lord did for us. We were driving

00:02:54.879 --> 00:02:58.390
down there when her water broke. We

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:01.110
got to the hospital, and the doctor

00:03:01.110 --> 00:03:01.120
asked,

00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:03.350
'Do you have any contractions? Do

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:05.509
you have any pain?'My wife

00:03:05.519 --> 00:03:07.509
said, 'No, not really. I don't

00:03:07.519 --> 00:03:10.949
feel anything.'The

00:03:10.949 --> 00:03:10.959
doctor

00:03:10.959 --> 00:03:13.430
said, 'There's

00:03:13.440 --> 00:03:15.110
no way you're in labor because

00:03:15.110 --> 00:03:15.120
of

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:16.630
the way you're

00:03:16.630 --> 00:03:16.640
acting.'There

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:20.070
was so much peace on her.

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:25.750
She

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:27.270
checked her and

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:29.509
said, 'Your water has

00:03:29.519 --> 00:03:31.350
broken, and

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:33.589
you're already dilated so

00:03:33.599 --> 00:03:35.670
far. This is really

00:03:35.670 --> 00:03:35.680
strange.'We

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:38.229
got up to

00:03:38.239 --> 00:03:40.550
the hospital room,

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:43.350
and

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:45.190
my wife was having contractions over and

00:03:45.190 --> 00:03:45.200
over—you

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:46.309
could see her stomach

00:03:46.309 --> 00:03:46.319
move—but

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:48.229
she had no pain. I

00:03:48.229 --> 00:03:48.239
was

00:03:48.239 --> 00:03:49.830
praying and could

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:51.670
see the

00:03:51.680 --> 00:03:53.270
contractions.

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:56.309
The Lord opened my eyes

00:03:56.309 --> 00:03:56.319
to

00:03:56.319 --> 00:03:58.229
the spirit realm, and I saw an

00:03:58.239 --> 00:04:01.110
angel standing with her with his hand on

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:03.589
her belly. I told my wife,

00:04:03.599 --> 00:04:04.949
'This is what I'm seeing in the

00:04:04.959 --> 00:04:07.350
spirit realm right now. This is

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:09.830
why you're not

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.509
feeling any

00:04:11.509 --> 00:04:11.519
pain.'The

00:04:11.519 --> 00:04:13.589
angel had his hand on

00:04:13.599 --> 00:04:16.390
her belly the whole time. She

00:04:16.390 --> 00:04:16.400
was

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:19.110
dilated all the way to a six or seven, yet

00:04:19.110 --> 00:04:19.120
she had

00:04:19.120 --> 00:04:23.430
no pain

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:26.070
at all, completely at peace

00:04:26.080 --> 00:04:28.950
as she was having our child.

00:04:28.960 --> 00:04:30.710
Family members came in and

00:04:30.710 --> 00:04:30.720
asked if she

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:32.550
had

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:35.430
an epidural. We said no.

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:40.469
They

00:04:40.479 --> 00:04:41.909
couldn't believe it; it

00:04:41.909 --> 00:04:41.919
was

00:04:41.919 --> 00:04:43.830
way out there for

00:04:43.830 --> 00:04:43.840
them.

00:04:43.840 --> 00:04:46.310
All of a sudden,

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:49.749
I started

00:04:49.759 --> 00:04:51.909
getting into fear about what was

00:04:51.919 --> 00:04:53.830
happening because of all the

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:55.350
doubt and unbelief coming

00:04:55.350 --> 00:04:55.360
into

00:04:55.360 --> 00:04:57.030
the room. People were saying, 'This is

00:04:57.040 --> 00:04:59.110
not possible.'The doctor was

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:01.110
freaked out and didn't understand,

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.950
and I let the doubt and unbelief

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:04.710
in.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:09.029
What happened next reminds

00:05:09.029 --> 00:05:09.039
me of

00:05:09.039 --> 00:05:12.150
when Peter was

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:15.189
walking on the water. He

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:18.870
was

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:22.390
able to make it so far until fear

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:24.710
gripped him; then he sank, and

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:26.870
Jesus had to

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:28.469
pick him up and put him back in the

00:05:28.479 --> 00:05:31.990
boat. It was a short span of faith that

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:34.950
got him there. Suddenly, when I

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:38.150
let fear in the room, pain started

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:40.150
hitting my wife. She

00:05:40.160 --> 00:05:41.430
started screaming; she was feeling

00:05:41.440 --> 00:05:44.390
it. That angel took his hand off.

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.029
I said, 'What are you

00:05:47.039 --> 00:05:48.469
doing? Put your hand back on

00:05:48.479 --> 00:05:51.110
my wife and help her!'I was angry and

00:05:51.110 --> 00:05:51.120
fearful

00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:53.990
at the same time.

00:05:53.990 --> 00:05:54.000
Suddenly,

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:56.950
that angel disappeared. My wife

00:05:56.960 --> 00:06:01.110
went from having no pain at all to

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:03.110
complete birthing pains. It

00:06:03.110 --> 00:06:03.120
was intense.

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:05.590
She started screaming

00:06:05.600 --> 00:06:07.270
in pain, which freaked me out

00:06:07.280 --> 00:06:09.590
even more. She

00:06:09.590 --> 00:06:09.600
cried,

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:11.110
'Oh my God, help me,

00:06:11.110 --> 00:06:11.120
Brandon!

00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:14.070
Help me! Help me!'I said,

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:15.270
'I don't know what to do. He

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:16.710
took his hand off you because there was

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:18.070
fear and doubt in

00:06:18.070 --> 00:06:18.080
the room.'Remember how

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:20.870
Jesus

00:06:20.870 --> 00:06:20.880
made

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:22.629
the people

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:24.950
leave

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:26.950
before He raised the girl

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:29.430
from the dead? It affected the

00:06:29.440 --> 00:06:31.990
atmosphere so much because of other

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:34.469
people's doubt and unbelief. You have to

00:06:34.479 --> 00:06:37.909
be very cautious about who you let inside your

00:06:37.919 --> 00:06:41.110
room. If you're sick in the hospital or

00:06:41.110 --> 00:06:41.120
facing an

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:44.309
incurable disease, and you

00:06:44.309 --> 00:06:44.319
let

00:06:44.319 --> 00:06:46.390
doubt and unbelief in—letting

00:06:46.390 --> 00:06:46.400
people

00:06:46.400 --> 00:06:49.029
speak

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:51.830
trash like 'this

00:06:51.840 --> 00:06:53.830
is

00:06:55.350 --> 00:06:55.360
impossible'—you

00:06:57.520 --> 00:06:58.950
need to send them out.

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:02.390
Say, 'No, this is a room of faith,

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:05.029
hope,

00:07:05.029 --> 00:07:05.039
and

00:07:05.039 --> 00:07:07.749
belief. I'm not going to let your

00:07:07.759 --> 00:07:10.950
trash come inside my hospital room.'You

00:07:10.950 --> 00:07:10.960
have

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:13.189
to send that stuff out. If Jesus

00:07:13.189 --> 00:07:13.199
were

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:16.469
on this earth today,

00:07:16.479 --> 00:07:18.550
would He send you out of the room?

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:21.110
That's what you have to think.

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:22.710
I want to be the one He says

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:24.870
can stay because my faith is strong

00:07:24.880 --> 00:07:26.790
and I'm believing with Him for the

00:07:26.800 --> 00:07:28.790
dead to be raised, for cancer to leave, and for

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:31.110
incurable diseases to be

00:07:31.110 --> 00:07:31.120
healed. You must

00:07:31.120 --> 00:07:33.909
have people

00:07:33.909 --> 00:07:33.919
of

00:07:33.919 --> 00:07:37.029
faith around you at all times.

00:07:37.039 --> 00:07:39.350
You can't allow doubt and unbelief to

00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:42.950
come in because the Bible says you can

00:07:42.960 --> 00:07:45.589
have whatever things you say, and

00:07:45.589 --> 00:07:45.599
what

00:07:45.599 --> 00:07:47.589
you say out of your mouth

00:07:47.589 --> 00:07:47.599
starts

00:07:47.599 --> 00:07:49.350
manifesting around

00:07:49.360 --> 00:07:52.150
you. If fear comes

00:07:52.150 --> 00:07:52.160
in,

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:54.469
fear starts to

00:07:54.479 --> 00:07:56.230
manifest. That's what happened in

00:07:56.240 --> 00:07:58.309
our case. We were robbed of a

00:07:58.319 --> 00:08:01.029
supernatural childbirth because of fear

00:08:01.039 --> 00:08:03.189
coming into the room—first from the doctor,

00:08:03.199 --> 00:08:05.270
then from the family.

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:07.029
What I should have done was tell

00:08:07.039 --> 00:08:08.869
the family, "I'm

00:08:08.869 --> 00:08:08.879
sorry."Then

00:08:08.879 --> 00:08:11.110
people from the church started coming.

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:12.710
"We ain't never seen nothing like this

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:15.350
before in our

00:08:15.350 --> 00:08:15.360
life."They

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:16.629
start doubting,

00:08:16.639 --> 00:08:18.390
and all that doubt starts

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:21.589
there. Doubt is a robber of your

00:08:21.599 --> 00:08:24.070
blessing. I

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:25.589
should have had authority and said,

00:08:25.599 --> 00:08:27.189
"You know what, y'all? I appreciate you

00:08:27.199 --> 00:08:29.189
coming by, but right now we're

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:31.430
having a

00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:34.870
baby here. Go on out of here."So that

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:36.709
angel disappeared; I didn't see it in

00:08:36.719 --> 00:08:38.469
the spirit realm anymore. My wife

00:08:38.479 --> 00:08:41.990
was dilated; she was at a five or

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:43.829
six, or

00:08:43.839 --> 00:08:45.110
maybe

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:48.230
an eight

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:48.870
or

00:08:48.880 --> 00:08:50.949
nine. The doctor said,

00:08:50.959 --> 00:08:53.430
"You're too far into it to get

00:08:53.430 --> 00:08:53.440
an

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:55.750
epidural. There's no

00:08:55.760 --> 00:08:57.670
turning back."The rest of

00:08:57.680 --> 00:09:00.310
the birthing process was bad,

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:01.910
but she had the baby and

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:04.310
everything was fine. My daughter's

00:09:04.310 --> 00:09:04.320
Apgar

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:06.070
scores were fine. Everything was fine.

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:08.150
It was just

00:09:08.160 --> 00:09:10.710
one of those moments that I learned a

00:09:10.720 --> 00:09:12.870
lot from. Your mountain needs to hear

00:09:12.880 --> 00:09:15.110
your voice. I'll say that again. You

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:16.949
need to know that: your mountain needs

00:09:16.959 --> 00:09:19.590
to hear your voice. You have to speak to

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:22.870
your circumstances.

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:24.949
My

00:09:24.959 --> 00:09:26.870
main thing I want to get across is

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:29.430
you have to be very cautious who you

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.990
allow inside of your inner circle.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:34.310
Whenever you're going through a trial or

00:09:34.310 --> 00:09:34.320
hard

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:37.910
circumstances,

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:41.750
you need to put a door up and

00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:44.949
say, "We are only allowing faith in

00:09:44.949 --> 00:09:44.959
here."Oral

00:09:44.959 --> 00:09:46.949
Roberts, because my wife graduated

00:09:46.959 --> 00:09:51.509
from ORU, said, "Make no little plans

00:09:51.519 --> 00:09:55.110
here. You've got to think big. You've

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.910
got to believe big."It

00:09:57.910 --> 00:09:57.920
was

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:01.190
everywhere: "Make

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:03.910
no little plans

00:10:03.910 --> 00:10:03.920
here."You've

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:05.990
got to

00:10:05.990 --> 00:10:06.000
have

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:10.389
a bulldog faith to grab onto a

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:12.710
bone and say, "I'm not going to let go

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:16.150
of what God has told me I can

00:10:16.150 --> 00:10:16.160
have."Anything

00:10:16.160 --> 00:10:20.069
that's in that

00:10:20.069 --> 00:10:20.079
word—anything—you

00:10:20.079 --> 00:10:23.590
find it, and he tells you

00:10:23.590 --> 00:10:23.600
that

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.990
you can have it. You can

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:28.710
achieve anything the word tells you you

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:33.110
can have. Do not let doubt and unbelief

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:36.389
rob you of your blessing.

00:10:36.399 --> 00:10:38.470
Stand when there's

00:10:38.470 --> 00:10:38.480
nothing

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:40.470
else to do but stand. Stand

00:10:40.480 --> 00:10:43.110
therefore and believe him for the

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:45.829
impossible. Believe him and you can

00:10:45.839 --> 00:10:47.829
achieve all things.

00:10:47.839 --> 00:10:50.870
I've seen it; I've seen God do things

00:10:50.870 --> 00:10:50.880
I never

00:10:50.880 --> 00:10:53.190
thought he

00:10:53.190 --> 00:10:53.200
would.

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:55.350
In my

00:10:55.350 --> 00:10:55.360
mind,

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:56.470
I always thought, "Well, it's

00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:58.389
going to happen this way. My

00:10:58.399 --> 00:11:01.590
miracle is going to happen this

00:11:01.590 --> 00:11:01.600
way."Don't

00:11:01.600 --> 00:11:04.550
limit God because he always comes

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:06.470
through in a way that you don't realize

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:07.990
he's going to, through

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:09.590
finances and all kinds of stuff.

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:11.910
When we didn't have

00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:15.030
any money to get groceries and you

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:16.389
think, "Well, it's going to come this

00:11:16.389 --> 00:11:16.399
way,"no,

00:11:16.399 --> 00:11:19.670
God comes through in ways

00:11:19.680 --> 00:11:22.310
that you can't even imagine. He'll use

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:25.030
whoever he needs to use, whoever is going

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:27.990
to be obedient. He has a million

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:29.829
and one ways to get it to you. It's

00:11:29.839 --> 00:11:31.910
going to happen if you just believe and

00:11:31.920 --> 00:11:35.350
don't give up. God's faithful to his

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:36.870
promises.

00:11:36.880 --> 00:11:38.470
So, I just wanted to give you that

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:41.190
encouragement today and tell you that

00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:44.230
Jesus is on the throne. He loves you.

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:46.630
Keep a smile on your face and a song in

00:11:46.640 --> 00:11:48.790
your heart. Thank you for being a

00:11:48.800 --> 00:11:51.350
part of my little family here, and God

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:55.200
bless you guys. Thank you. Bye-bye.

